ana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr2_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000366_fr2.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr2-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000366_fr1_rear_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 13.05.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr1_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000366_fr1_rear.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 13.05.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr1_rear-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\" src=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based upon photograph, after Korhonen\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>(tomb) of Gaius Pompeius Felix and Scribonia Restituta\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Given that both names reflect senatorial families attested in the area, this is assumed to be a freedman and freedwoman of the families. Korhonen notes the absence of 'Dis Manibus' as encouraging a first-century date, alongside the palaeography. Castelli and Ferrara report the right fragment only as a separate text, in addition to reporting the entire text, following a notice in Amico.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Amico 1741 225 no.29 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Castelli 1769 182 no. 102 (269 no.46) \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Castelli 1784 192 no. 117 (288 no.47) \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrara 1829 358 no. 4 (380 no.3) \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mommsen 1883 \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7084\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 119 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp